                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 20437/83.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Ambassador</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-05-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 11, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reichstag passed potash law last evening. It empowers Bundesrat to reduce prices
                    on contracts prior to December 17, 1909, so that on deliveries after May 1,
                    1910, the prices, duty included, shall not be higher than those prevailing
                    before June 30, 1909.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hill.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
